data.description: Luxury is what you will find in this beautiful 3-story townhome. Enjoy resort style living, just steps away from the clubhouse with 5 pools, playgrounds, basketball and tennis courts. If open floorplans are your thing, you will be at home in this kitchen, featuring a large island that can seat up to 6 people, stainless steel appliances, and tons of natural lighting. This townhome with garage boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, and outdoor deck to enjoy those warm summer evenings that are right around the corner. Freshly painted with new carpet on upper level. This home is a must see!  Don't miss out on this beauty that's only 2 years old.  Owner had the house appraised by a licensed, certified real estate appraiser.  Appraisal came in at $419,900.00!  Don't miss this fabulous deal as owner is listing for $10,000.00 below appraisal at $409,900.00!
